BT /F1 10 Tf 82 474 Td (\(per-record data key wrapped by a KMS master key\).) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 448 Td (Detokenization requires a mutually authenticated mTLS call plus a scoped service identity;) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 434 Td (no batch detokenization is permitted.) Tj ET
