BT /F1 10 Tf 82 390 Td (The design keeps raw PANs out of all downstream analytics stores, narrowing PCI-DSS scope) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 376 Td (to the vault and tokenization service. Target throughput: 45,000 tokenizations/sec at p99) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 362 Td (< 12ms. Keys rotate every 90 days with overlapping validity to avoid the propagation) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 348 Td (failure mode seen in INC-2026-0419. Security sign-off is required before any change to the) Tj ET
